According to the police report, the suspect Zhang is an outsider and suffers from mental disorder.

On the morning of May 15, a large number of people gathered at Minsheng Bank on Jianshe Road, Heping District, Tianjin, to demand the return of their houses.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 15, a building in Guangzhou was in protest because the underground recycling station next to the community that was originally promised to be used for recycling waste was turned into an ordinary garbage station. This triggered a conflict between the owners and the police, and some owners were taken away.
